Package: predictCheckR
Title: Bayesian Posterior Predictive Checking Utilities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    given  = "predictCheckR",
    family = "Maintainer",
    email  = "maintainer@example.com",
    role   = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description: Provides a suite of utilities for Bayesian posterior predictive
    checking using the bayesplot ecosystem. Functions cover the full workflow:
    generating posterior predictive samples from draws matrices, computing
    predictive discrepancy statistics (Bayesian p-values, RMSE, coverage),
    producing publication-ready diagnostic plots, and comparing competing
    models via predictive performance metrics. Outputs are compatible with
    draw matrices produced by 'brms' and 'rstan'.
